<div class="riskr-investors">

  <div class="riskr-investors__hero page-width">
    <p class="riskr-investors__eyebrow">Investor Relations</p>
    <h1 class="riskr-investors__headline">
      Delivering shareholder value,<br>one shirt at a time.
    </h1>
    <p class="riskr-investors__subhead">
      Riskr Inc. is committed to transparency, accountability, and the responsible materialization of enterprise-grade synergies across all business units.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="riskr-investors__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-investors__metrics page-width">
    <div class="riskr-investors__metric">
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-number">Q1 2026</span>
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-label">Current Fiscal Quarter</span>
    </div>
    <div class="riskr-investors__metric">
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-number">+∞%</span>
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-label">YoY Synergy Growth</span>
    </div>
    <div class="riskr-investors__metric">
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-number">$0.00</span>
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-label">Debt (Strategic)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="riskr-investors__metric">
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-number">100%</span>
      <span class="riskr-investors__metric-label">Alignment Score</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="riskr-investors__divider"></div>

  <div class="riskr-investors__body page-width">

    <div class="riskr-investors__section">
      <div class="riskr-investors__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-investors__label">Investment Thesis</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-investors__content-col">
        <p>We operate at the convergence of two powerful macro trends: the continued professionalization of personal branding, and the global demand for cotton-based deliverables.</p>
        <p>Our go-to-market strategy is simple: identify professionals who need to signal ambition, manufacture garments that facilitate that signaling, and deliver them in a box with tissue paper.</p>
        <p>We believe this is a trillion-dollar opportunity. Our analysts agree. Our analysts are us.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-investors__divider riskr-investors__divider--inner"></div>

    <div class="riskr-investors__section">
      <div class="riskr-investors__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-investors__label">Financial Highlights</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-investors__content-col">
        <div class="riskr-investors__table">
          <div class="riskr-investors__table-row riskr-investors__table-row--header">
            <span>Metric</span>
            <span>FY2025</span>
            <span>FY2026 (Projected)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-investors__table-row">
            <span>Revenue</span>
            <span>Confidential</span>
            <span>More</span>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-investors__table-row">
            <span>EBITDA</span>
            <span>Positive (eventually)</span>
            <span>Increasingly positive</span>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-investors__table-row">
            <span>Burn Rate</span>
            <span>Sustainable</span>
            <span>Also sustainable</span>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-investors__table-row">
            <span>Runway</span>
            <span>Adequate</span>
            <span>Longer</span>
          </div>
          <div class="riskr-investors__table-row">
            <span>Net Promoter Score</span>
            <span>High</span>
            <span>Higher</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-investors__divider riskr-investors__divider--inner"></div>

    <div class="riskr-investors__section">
      <div class="riskr-investors__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-investors__label">Risk Factors</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-investors__content-col">
        <p>Investing in Riskr involves a high degree of risk. You should carefully consider the following factors before making any investment decision:</p>
        <ul class="riskr-investors__risk-list">
          <li>The market for corporate satire apparel may contract if irony becomes scarce</li>
          <li>Cotton prices are subject to fluctuation based on weather, trade policy, and vibes</li>
          <li>Key personnel may achieve full enlightenment and leave the corporate paradigm entirely</li>
          <li>Synergies, once materialized, may dematerialize</li>
          <li>The concept of "alignment" may be exposed as inherently meaningless</li>
          <li>Competitors may also start making shirts</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="riskr-investors__disclaimer">This page does not constitute a securities offering. Riskr Inc. is not publicly traded. Please consult your financial advisor, your life coach, and your LinkedIn network before making any decisions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="riskr-investors__divider riskr-investors__divider--inner"></div>

    <div class="riskr-investors__section">
      <div class="riskr-investors__label-col">
        <span class="riskr-investors__label">Contact IR</span>
      </div>
      <div class="riskr-investors__content-col">
        <p>For investor inquiries, partnership discussions, or requests to be added to our capitalization table in a non-binding capacity, please reach out to our Investor Relations department.</p>
        <a href="mailto:ir@riskr.inc" class="riskr-investors__link">
          ir@riskr.inc <span class="riskr-investors__link-arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .riskr-investors {
    background: #fff;
  }

  .riskr-investors__hero {
    padding-block: 100px 80px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__headline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__subhead {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.52);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .riskr-investors__divider {
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }

  .riskr-investors__divider--inner {
    margin-block: 0;
  }

  .riskr-investors__metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    padding-block: 64px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__metric-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading--family);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .riskr-investors__metric-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .riskr-investors__body {
    padding-block: 0 80px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 0 80px;
    padding-block: 72px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__label-col {
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .riskr-investors__content-col p {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__content-col p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .riskr-investors__table {
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__table-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-block: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
  }

  .riskr-investors__table-row--header {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
  }

  .riskr-investors__risk-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__risk-list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
    padding: 10px 0 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .riskr-investors__risk-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .riskr-investors__disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.75rem !important;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38) !important;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 24px !important;
  }

  .riskr-investors__link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-body--family);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .riskr-investors__link-arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .riskr-investors__link:hover .riskr-investors__link-arrow {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .riskr-investors__metrics {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .riskr-investors__section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      padding-block: 56px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .riskr-investors__hero {
      padding-block: 72px 56px;
    }

    .riskr-investors__metrics {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      padding-block: 48px;
    }

    .riskr-investors__table-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .riskr-investors__table-row span:last-child {
      display: none;
    }

    .riskr-investors__table-row--header span:last-child {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Riskr Investors",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "riskr-investors-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Riskr Investors"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
